About the Business

Don't eat at Delish Pizza, unless you want pizza that will blow your mind! Conceded Facts: Delish Pizza: Our dough gets prepared daily from scratch using secretly prepared dough starters and given a 24 hour fermentation process for a light, airy and crispy crusts. Delish Pizza: Sauces made fresh every morning from scratch using locally sourced tomato, locally sourced CA cold pressed olive oi;, topped with fresh basil and other secret spices that will make your taste buds dance. Delish Pizza: Ranch and white sauce tasting so good, it might make you want to slap your mamma. "But Don't" Delish Pizza: Has been voted #1 by Yelp in Sacramento 3 years in a row. Moral: Eat Delish Pizza!…

Frequently Asked Questions about Delish Pizza

Does Delish Pizza take reservations?

Yes, you can make a reservation by picking a date, time, and party size.

Is Delish Pizza currently offering delivery or takeout?

Yes, Delish Pizza offers both delivery and takeout.

What forms of payment are accepted?
